486
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:15,380
Oh, Encik Ular, ini awak.

487
00:34:16,030 --> 00:34:18,130
Saya fikir bos ada di sini. Awak takutkan saya.

488
00:34:23,630 --> 00:34:24,630
